Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.52,0:00:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}千夏字幕組製作  翻譯：lia  校對：馬忽悠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.05,0:00:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（歡迎來到白流村 由此向前50米 旅店NIWA）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.24,0:00:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大自然富饒而寧靜 空氣很乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.59,0:00:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樸素的氣氛很好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.70,0:00:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以食物新鮮而美味
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特別是剛生下的來的雞蛋 可說是極品中的極品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.31,0:00:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我家住宿的客人大家都這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.85,0:00:40.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說實話在這裡住了16年真是吃膩了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:19.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（第一話 風之露天咖啡館）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.74,0:02:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利繪親 早上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.84,0:02:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安 小夜前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.34,0:02:36.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杏裡前輩 春乃前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你出那麼多汗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為不甘心啊 只有我騎自行車
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.53,0:02:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也是我們走過的路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.12,0:02:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我這種不坐摩托來就會遲到的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春乃的家裡確實如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.54,0:03:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了告別這種悲慘的人生 到了16歲立刻拿到駕駛證
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我到那時候哦 可愛的小祖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.42,0:03:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（本田祖瑪摩托車 Honda zuma）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.42,0:03:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出來了 最愛祖瑪宣言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.31,0:03:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜前輩 不是祖瑪而是小祖 我有商品說明書呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.51,0:03:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杏裡前輩 春乃前輩也來看看 很可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.65,0:03:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 春乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.87,0:03:24.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 要冰一下這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（臨時調查 二學年 1將來想做的職業 2不限制於職業想要做的事）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是個調查 不能考慮得很複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:39.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你對我這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.83,0:03:44.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離交上來還有三分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.69,0:03:53.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（想去大城市）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:04:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦～　會來新人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就到繁忙的季節了 可能會人手不足
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狀態真好呢 小祖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次會來什麼樣的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.15,0:04:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.92,0:04:14.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出現個像電影裡那樣的管家什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.53,0:04:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.68,0:04:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管家…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（想像中的有錢人）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春乃大小姐 您能要吃飯還是洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.21,0:04:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掃除 洗衣服 準備客房 照看雞棚 我都做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.67,0:04:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（不切實際的想像）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論作業還是備考都交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.91,0:04:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白日夢做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇到完美的管家了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又白日做夢了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.12,0:04:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但還真是值得期待
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正馬上就會走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.11,0:04:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後都會說 在自然中重獲自我了什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.87,0:05:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？ 去哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先要去看看是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 去我家？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:09.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我給哥哥發個短信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:12.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說真的…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.86,0:05:35.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,風
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:40.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是從今天開始在我們這裡幹活的辛西婭.B.羅傑斯小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.82,0:05:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在網上認識的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.81,0:05:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇　都是些非常可愛的孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:05:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼語
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,含著好幾種
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.58,0:06:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 稍微有些抱歉 這身衣服太緊了骨頭痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於輕鬆了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.96,0:06:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶吶 外面的CBR是誰的 大波
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.96,0:06:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（本田CBR系列摩托）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.55,0:06:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又增加了個可愛的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝哥哥的福利照片Get
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,印度風意大利面 紐約風調味 越南風配菜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.48,0:06:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底是哪國風的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是多國式的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛西婭騎著摩托車去過很多國家旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真帥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.26,0:06:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,please 嘗嘗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.56,0:06:55.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是… 雜交在一起的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:06:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前所未聞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努力做的話會能吃的 大概
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鑒於好評連連 奉上第二彈...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋澆飯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要攪拌下吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.94,0:07:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦～ 好吃極了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本的簡樸嫻靜美妙極了 非常感激ing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.81,0:07:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到這地步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春乃大神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢當不敢當
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:00.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛西婭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該說是誤會 但她應該不是壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得她和我不一樣不適合這小村子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 春乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm coming
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛西婭 為什麼你會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.89,0:08:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從汐崎真子那裡聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.00,0:08:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It'好耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.70,0:00:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鰻魚蓋飯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:48.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Pretty Good
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.12,0:08:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明這是唯一能讓自己獨處的地點 可惡的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.31,0:08:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春乃真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:08:59.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是這茶 還有這Great view
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.03,0:09:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有蛋澆飯 告訴了我至今為止沒見過的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 並不是我厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.39,0:09:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如說去過很多國家的辛西婭才厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春乃也要去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.48,0:09:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是… 不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能？ 為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問我為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行就是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.67,0:09:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行就是不行嗎 我是從何時開始這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春乃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Another cup 多汁的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再來一碗吧 好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑向任何地方一直都是直線
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:51.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有人家什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美國的中西部確實是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:10:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But 在中途不知不覺就到晚上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.89,0:10:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想著在那裡露營
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狼好可怕 嗚嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.74,0:10:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.61,0:10:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 真是愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.12,0:10:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很愉快嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用摩托車和狼賽跑感覺真好 真愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界延伸到外面 嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果總是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:39.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定不可能了 反正是不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.15,0:10:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後在岸邊還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.47,0:10:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汽艇就開始下沉了 不盡全力跳的話就沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,認為不可能也只有上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.29,0:11:04.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別介意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和往常一樣的白日夢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:12.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又做夢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.58,0:11:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是天真浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.96,0:11:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我也要像辛西婭一樣衝向外國
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes you can
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.92,0:11:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和小祖走遍世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（Yes we can，Yes I can，Yes you can 一二 Yes…）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這份心情是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我知道並不是所有想做的事情都能夠實現
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以做的事情一定不值一提
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.11,0:11:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算從這裡逃出去也一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 難道說我是羨慕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.01,0:11:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺自己真渺小
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.19,0:12:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上起來腦袋就這麼懈怠 一定是晚上做夢的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜取得了諾貝爾文學獎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏成了大作曲家 利繪親騎著大摩托飛上天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我卻在給大家送雞蛋 真是搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.85,0:12:28.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然因為辛西婭的原因 茶館變得每天都熙熙攘攘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這兩三天還算過的安穩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.95,0:12:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春乃 我今天一定會做好的 你看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.70,0:12:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.89,0:12:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good moring夫人們 我來取蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.75,0:12:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,stop stop hurry up
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我不會饒了你們 看招 呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:12:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 你們這群膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.60,0:13:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經完了嗎 Come on
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛西婭 我有點著急
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.69,0:13:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.36,0:13:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走好 春乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（第二話 春之序曲）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.71,0:13:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 就是這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.49,0:13:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要說和之前不一樣的地方大概就只有我的工作增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.97,0:13:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏真是的 這不是什麼好笑的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.09,0:13:30.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.68,0:13:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才來沒幾天 過些日子就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也不是什麼壞人 就當做好事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小祖當然不錯 要環遊世界果然要用大摩托啊 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茂登屋摩托行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這附近的人無論是買摩托還是修摩托大都來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們從小時候就熟知
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:08.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且它離學校比較近 還有能消閒的咖啡館
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.02,0:14:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們四個人放學後總是不知不覺走到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利繪親 你要環遊世界是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:18.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes 當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很美妙嗎 騎著摩托去美國什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.64,0:14:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騎著小祖？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢 果然還是小祖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要和狼賽跑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.65,0:14:34.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 那果然還是用大的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.74,0:14:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 這裡還是相信小祖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.25,0:14:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都說了不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太受辛西婭影響了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.47,0:14:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然你這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 不瞞你說我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.10,0:14:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（我做環遊世界的旅行）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.09,0:14:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連小夜也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看你看 春乃前輩也坦率點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:14:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坦率嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼什麼 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想聽我昨天做的曲子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想聽想聽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.08,0:15:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請欣賞 feat.愛犬麻呂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:13.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 麻呂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.87,0:15:21.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻呂的伴奏真完美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.43,0:15:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家在聽曲子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在聽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總是感覺和平時的氛圍不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著辛西婭的話就來了靈感
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.71,0:15:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂的 在聽她說話的時候有種刺激的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.91,0:15:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是就辛西婭的印象來說這是不是有些太可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切切切 你不懂呢 瞄準兩者間的差距才是來靈感的訣竅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.92,0:16:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為有過去那個風姿綽約的金子銀子 所以才有現在的形象
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.88,0:16:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來靈感…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:07.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣 曲子完成了再多多關照 春乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杏裡前輩的專屬歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.22,0:16:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 有是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己和麻呂一起唱不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 歌要春乃唱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.71,0:16:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這規定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.51,0:16:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從你納涼歌唱大賽史上最年輕的獲獎者的那天開始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊 不要輸給麻呂 春乃前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.28,0:16:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標進軍米國 世界最強人氣...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.54,0:16:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 羞死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 吵到大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.87,0:16:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害羞就說明事實上春乃前輩也想那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:45.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前一直說呢 想成為歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.01,0:16:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌唱大賽也是夢想的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.64,0:16:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這樣 這是我的黑歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.53,0:17:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說了 在這種深山裡唱給誰聽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.32,0:17:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.91,0:17:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑了不少距離了 幫我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.08,0:17:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是挺乾淨的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我每天都自己檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.77,0:17:20.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛西婭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.62,0:17:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛西婭也一起來喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 加我一個加我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stop 在外面別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在聽曲子前先說好 畫面上有非常可愛的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.21,0:17:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我說你別叫出來恐怕也不太可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.81,0:17:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有三秒 剩下集中聽曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.02,0:17:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1 2 3 好的結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超very美妙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 得到好評了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.96,0:18:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到通向世界的護照了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是杏裡做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後春乃前輩要唱歌的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成後讓我聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:24.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這充滿幹勁的氣場是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.76,0:18:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶吶 辛西婭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騎著摩托車旅行的話 去哪裡好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.76,0:18:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去想去的地方就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.76,0:18:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想去的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.18,0:18:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是… 如果那種事能做到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係 你做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不決定目的地只是奔馳下去 一定會遇到美好的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.01,0:18:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要先試試看?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:52.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說這麼沒責任的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛西婭和我們不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼不一樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.48,0:19:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出身 養育方式 考慮方式什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.42,0:19:07.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大小之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.71,0:19:08.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛西婭是澳大利亞 而我們是小村子 大小不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.87,0:19:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛西婭騎普通的摩托車的話 而我們是助動車
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.71,0:19:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能做到的事很有限
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話是如此 但是利繪親暢談下夢想不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 而且春乃前輩如果把夢想說出口 它就可能會實現的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.77,0:19:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的歌只管用到歌唱大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.69,0:19:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我要把早上拿到的蔬菜送到家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.45,0:19:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛西婭還要呆到摩托車檢查完吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.84,0:19:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先回家了 大家再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.25,0:19:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.25,0:19:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.97,0:20:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那輛摩托和GIORNO相比
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.97,0:20:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（GIORNO:本田旗下車型）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.34,0:20:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最高速度完全不一樣吧 爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.00,0:20:25.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要看騎手了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.13,0:20:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我太奇怪了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.82,0:20:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和她的姐姐發生了什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.16,0:20:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並不是辛西婭的錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.53,0:20:40.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都騎不慣 應該是我的問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:44.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 太小了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.49,0:20:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的配件最初肯定都是磕磕碰碰的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.81,0:20:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要著急 慢慢磨合就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:20:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這麼回事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.98,0:21:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都被辛西婭影響了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.22,0:21:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,器量大小...就是這麼回事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.61,0:21:19.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好啊 春乃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 我是有預想到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.75,0:21:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,味增煮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春乃 我給你看個好東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.35,0:21:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是 麻呂？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.28,0:21:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去了小杏家麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.84,0:21:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh yes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.21,0:21:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天帶來了自己的杯子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.14,0:21:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是是吃麵用的...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.93,0:21:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.14,0:22:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不試試的話不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.91,0:22:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思 你就是為了說這句話才過來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.70,0:22:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.92,0:22:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是春乃的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.98,0:22:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜和杏裡和利繪也這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.20,0:22:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前 春乃一直這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.96,0:22:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.97,0:22:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春乃 去海邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.18,0:22:35.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海邊哦 海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個人去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.98,0:22:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.23,0:22:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.37,0:22:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈 你在說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.85,0:22:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.03,0:22:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不 媽媽她們會擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.84,0:22:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼小心點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.58,0:22:55.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以為你不會同意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.34,0:22:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.08,0:22:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜騎也是很特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.16,0:23:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.96,0:23:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛西婭 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.36,0:23:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK 交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.28,0:23:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你騎這個去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.58,0:23:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是喲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.45,0:23:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平時是我用的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.89,0:23:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狀態很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.63,0:23:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩人都騎車 才行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.81,0:23:28.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿餵狗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.17,0:23:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路順風
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.70,0:23:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一片黑完全看不見前面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.45,0:23:48.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 沒想像中那麼可怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.77,0:23:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是和辛西婭在一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.36,0:24:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.50,0:24:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速度也完全上不來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.88,0:24:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就保持這樣？可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.57,0:24:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明這麼慢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.67,0:24:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算這樣保持現狀就好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.21,0:24:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很努力呢 GIORNO
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.08,0:24:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就要看騎手了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.73,0:24:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前春乃一直這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.48,0:24:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.68,0:24:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是全是大人哦 沒可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.78,0:24:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不試試怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.56,0:24:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不試試怎麼知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.82,0:25:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能跑到多快 那全看我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.70,0:25:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 所以 反正都不可能的話
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.31,0:25:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從一開始別做就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.36,0:25:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一個人能做到的事是有限的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.69,0:25:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過到底跑了多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.84,0:25:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翻了幾個坡也根本看不到大海
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.27,0:25:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多就是極限了 該結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.92,0:25:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等翻過了那個坡就...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.28,0:25:38.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大海
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.71,0:25:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是大海
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.58,0:25:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是大海
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.15,0:26:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.69,0:26:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我會流淚
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.91,0:26:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.75,0:26:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超級好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.60,0:26:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛西婭 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.42,0:26:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到真的能看到大海
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.50,0:26:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是辛西婭的福
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.36,0:26:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？ 我有給春乃幫上忙麼
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.69,0:26:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 幫了很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.33,0:26:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.43,0:26:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然也再次感受到一個人什麼也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.56,0:26:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.51,0:26:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像辛西婭那樣什麼都做得到的人我覺得很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.76,0:26:51.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是一個人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.45,0:26:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也和大家都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.64,0:26:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.19,0:27:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借助了他們的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.57,0:27:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不止如此
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.03,0:27:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,製作摩托的人 製作道路的人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.31,0:27:12.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有各種各樣的人們 把我們帶到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.34,0:27:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅行的途中 一直都這麼想著
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.96,0:27:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,素未謀面的許多人們 給予了我力量
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.87,0:27:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我覺得自己能去到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.10,0:27:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春乃也是 不斷依靠他人就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.06,0:27:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春乃 Are you ok？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.55,0:27:51.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.93,0:27:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人 都濕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.66,0:27:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 不過馬上就干了吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.04,0:28:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不斷依靠他人就好
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.72,0:28:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我一直以來都不曾有過的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.93,0:28:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人們不是獨自一人
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.42,0:28:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這句肥皂劇裡的老套台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.47,0:28:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻不可思議地落在了心田里
